  Locus:
    Page: 463
    Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Surrender
---
When our motive is right, and when our heart is pure, our eye single, and
our faith in God -- that is, when we cast ourselves utterly and completely
upon the inner, sustaining Providential Power of the Universe -- then God
cannot fail us, something must happen.
